io.micronaut.annotation.processing

Class PackageConfigurationInjectProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.annotation.processing.AbstractProcessor
      • io.micronaut.annotation.processing.PackageConfigurationInjectProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Processor

    @SupportedAnnotationTypes(value="io.micronaut.context.annotation.Configuration")
 @SupportedSourceVersion(value=RELEASE_8)
 @Internal
public class PackageConfigurationInjectProcessor
extends AbstractProcessor
    An annotation processor that generates BeanConfiguration implementations for each package annotated with Configuration.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Graeme Rocher
